Recommendations:
We recommended that Management:
3.16 Establish Inventory Committee dedicated only to conduct physical count of Local Road Network;
3.17 Before conducting the physical count, the MAO and the MEO reconcile their records to ensure that the road network system recorded in the books is reflected in the Engineering Inventory of Road Network maintained by the MEO.
3.18 Thereafter, direct the Inventory Committee to start with the road network system recorded in the books. In the conduct of physical count, determine each component of the local roads, its costs or fair market value (if without identified costs);
3.19 Direct the inventory committee to prepare the Physical Count Report on the Local Road Network and;
